# This repo intentionally tracks TamTam agent/config files. Override global
# ignore rules that may ignore the whole .tamtam directory, but keep generated
# runtime cache out of commits.
!.tamtam/
!.tamtam/.gitignore
!.tamtam/config.yml
!.tamtam/agents/
!.tamtam/agents/*.md
.tamtam/cache/
